. zero-trust) model for AI and suggest a set of\nproperties that should be satisfied to ensure the trustworthiness of AI\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Jun 2022 21:13:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-27"}
