 do evolve to optimize learning environments and that the\nerection of the dichotomy \"traditional instruction versus active learning\" is\nno longer relevant.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Jun 2022 08:20:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Oct 2022 06:50:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-20"}
