nce of nearly spanning cycles, our fourth result determines,\nunder milder conditions, the correct order of magnitude of the size of the\nrandom perturbation required to ensure that a.a.s. $G$ contains such a cycle.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Jun 2022 10:49:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-27"}
